column2: SELECT TOP #  s.z as zz, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z FROM photoprimary AS p JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE   p.modelMagErr_u < #  AND p.modelMagErr_g < #  AND p.modelMagErr_r < #  AND p.modelMagErr_i < #  AND p.modelMagErr_z < #  AND s.Class = &&&  AND s.zErr < #  AND p.type = #  AND p.probPSF < #  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #
